com.hazelcast.jet.datamodel

Class TimestampedItem<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.jet.datamodel.TimestampedItem<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the item
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class TimestampedItem<T>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a data item with the event timestamp added to it. Used in the Pipeline API as the default data type to emit from global windowed aggregation stages (those that aggregate all the data in a window, without grouping).
